  <entry>
    <id>https://github.com/stonith404/pingvin-share/releases/tag/v0.22.1</id>
    <title>New release for Pingvin Share: v0.22.1</title>
    <updated>2024-02-18T15:53:25-05:00</updated>
    <author>
      <name>stonith404/pingvin-share</name>
    </author>
    <content>&lt;p&gt;⚠️ &lt;strong&gt;For stand-alone installations&lt;/strong&gt;: If the backend of Pingvin Share isn't running on &lt;code&gt;http://localhost:8080&lt;/code&gt;, you have to set the &lt;code&gt;API_URL&lt;/code&gt; environment variable like &lt;a href="https://github.com/stonith404/pingvin-share?tab=readme-ov-file#stand-alone"&gt;mentioned in the docs&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Bug Fixes&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;wrong back links on error modals (&lt;a href="https://github.com/stonith404/pingvin-share/commit/f52dffdaac5a893804525913943f3f4f99b7c55a"&gt;f52dffd&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;prevent zoom on input field click on mobile (&lt;a href="https://github.com/stonith404/pingvin-share/commit/9c734ec439aeaeebe172caa41bf531e6d8b3fac3"&gt;9c734ec&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;replace middleware backend url with local backend url (&lt;a href="https://github.com/stonith404/pingvin-share/commit/76df6f66d965dd751146468abfafb0c6acd46310"&gt;76df6f6&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;user &lt;code&gt;id&lt;/code&gt; and &lt;code&gt;totpVerified&lt;/code&gt; can be changed by user (&lt;a href="https://github.com/stonith404/pingvin-share/commit/e663da45b1d15f5e6e33118e6a28e1504688034c"&gt;e663da4&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;user enumaration on forgot password page (&lt;a href="https://github.com/stonith404/pingvin-share/commit/64515d77cfc116a243d78610395ccc383ba62940"&gt;64515d7&lt;/a&gt;) reported by @massot-c&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</content>
    <link href="https://github.com/stonith404/pingvin-share/releases/tag/v0.22.1" rel="alternate"/>
  </entry>
