      <name>stonith404/pingvin-share</name>
    </author>
    <content>&lt;h3&gt;Features&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;add config variable to adjust chunk size (&lt;a href="https://github.com/stonith404/pingvin-share/commit/0bfbaea49aad0c695fee6558c89c661687912e4f"&gt;0bfbaea&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Bug Fixes&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;delete share files if user gets deleted (&lt;a href="https://github.com/stonith404/pingvin-share/commit/e71f6cd1598ed87366074398042a6b88675587ca"&gt;e71f6cd&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;error in logs if "allow unauthenticated shares" is enabled (&lt;a href="https://github.com/stonith404/pingvin-share/commit/c6d8188e4e33ba682551a3ca79205ff5a6d7ead5"&gt;c6d8188&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;memory leak while uploading files by disabling base64 encoding of chunks (&lt;a href="https://github.com/stonith404/pingvin-share/commit/7a15fbb4651c2fee32fb4c1ee2c9d7f12323feb0"&gt;7a15fbb&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Translations&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;add Ukrainian by @DmytroOnopa &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</content>
